{
  "chapter": 47,
  "chapter_summary": "第四十七回 缚龙索\n\n本章主要讲述了芮玮在魔鬼岛遭遇的一系列事件。伊吾国国师原氏兄弟向芮玮讲述了公主叶白被七情魔章痴抛弃后神智失常的往事。花衣女子（叶白）误将芮玮当作章痴，用迷魂巾将其迷倒并用缚龙索捆绑。叶青和简怀萱赶到试图解救芮玮，但缚龙索刀剑难断。岛主叶士谋出现，对芮玮的武功和相貌（与简召舞酷似）感到惊讶。叶青劝说父亲相信芮玮能治愈姐姐的病症，并警告简召舞可能已出卖魔鬼岛。果然，原氏兄弟发现三艘快船驶来，船上正是简召舞引来的七剑派高手。叶士谋大怒，将芮玮关押，准备迎敌。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_yuan_si_cong",
      "speaker_name": "原思聪",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "天堂有路不去，地狱无门自要来，小子，咱们又见面啦！",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 4,
      "line_end": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yuan_si_min",
      "speaker_name": "原思敏",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "凡事皆因强出头，到时招得祸满身……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 8,
      "line_end": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_yi_nv_zi",
      "speaker_name": "花衣女子",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "你骗了我的感情，骗了我的身体，当年的山盟海誓就忘得那么快吗……你想一走了之，不行，不行，决不行，今天我就不让你走了……",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 18,
      "line_end": 18
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yuan_si_cong",
      "speaker_name": "原思聪",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "小子看清楚没有？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 24,
      "line_end": 24
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_yuan_si_cong",
      "text": "这女子芮玮从未见过，胡说八道，敢情神智不清？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 26,
      "line_end": 26
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yuan_si_cong",
      "speaker_name": "原思聪",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "你能看出她神智不清就成啦。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 28,
      "line_end": 28
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_yuan_si_cong",
      "text": "这是什么意思？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 30,
      "line_end": 30
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yuan_si_cong",
      "speaker_name": "原思聪",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "你不认识咱们公主，对吗？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 32,
      "line_end": 32
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_yuan_si_cong",
      "text": "什么？她就是公主，叶青的姐姐？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 34,
      "line_end": 34
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yuan_si_cong",
      "speaker_name": "原思聪",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "你不认识她，那年你救的七情魔却认识她，而且识之甚稔。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 36,
      "line_end": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "七情魔已死其五，往昔他们兄弟若有对不起这位姑娘的地方，也就算了，唉！这世上情之一字本就勉强不得！",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 44,
      "line_end": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yuan_si_cong",
      "speaker_name": "原思聪",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "算了！有这等便宜的事，我们岛主的女儿岂是好欺负的，七情魔虽然死了五个，但还有两个是谁。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 48,
      "line_end": 50
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_yuan_si_cong",
      "text": "他们七兄弟间手足情深，死了兄弟悲痛可想而知，剩下两个你们难道还放不过吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 52,
      "line_end": 54
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yuan_si_cong",
      "speaker_name": "原思聪",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "你同情他们，就不同情我们公主……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 56,
      "line_end": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yuan_si_cong",
      "speaker_name": "原思聪",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "你看，这么个好女子，竟害得她疯颠，当年就是我兄弟俩陪着公主到江湖游历，未想到遇到章痴花言巧语地把她整个心骗去了……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 58,
      "line_end": 58
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yuan_si_cong",
      "speaker_name": "原思聪",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "公主自幼深居简出，在魔鬼岛上长大，第一次到江湖走动，那晓世情的险恶，章痴要追她本是好事，我兄弟也不敢阻止公主的意志。然而对一位清白女子忍心虚情假意吗，公主无知还被骗去了身体，这对她是何等重要的事，但章痴爱够了，玩腻了，竟把她抛弃，一走了之……",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 62,
      "line_end": 64
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yuan_si_cong",
      "speaker_name": "原思聪",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "公主不能忘情，苦苦追踪，总算有一天追到，你知不知道七情魔对公主说什么话吗？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 70,
      "line_end": 72
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yuan_si_cong",
      "speaker_name": "原思聪",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "我还记得清楚，葛恨说：不要脸的丫头，你追我们兄弟做什，找汉子也不是这样找法，要找去街上随便拉一个好啦，我们的性情闹云野鹤，谁也羁绊不了，你这臭丫头，快滚，快滚！你想这种话什么人能够忍受得了，公主一阵大笑就此气得神智失常，可怜迄今她还未能痊愈，只要见着生人就当她的爱人回来了……",
      "tone": "悲痛",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 76,
      "line_end": 78
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yuan_si_cong",
      "speaker_name": "原思聪",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "当时我兄弟只要章痴回心转意也不过问，我们可以回来禀告岛主将公主嫁给他，成就一桩好事。但那话实在令人气疯，我们不得不教训他们，七情魔空负盛名，数十招不到就被我兄弟俩用催眠术迷倒，然后将他们一个个从此打断了腿才弄醒。还是看在公主分上没敢重伤他们，弄醒后就劝章痴永远相伴公主，负个为人的责任。该他们命不该绝，却恰好让他们师门长辈经过救走，我们没法，只好带着失常的公主回来，还好岛主没深责。只略略告诫我们一番，我们免惩罚，但见公主终日哭哭无常心里怎生过意得去。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 82,
      "line_end": 90
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yuan_si_cong",
      "speaker_name": "原思聪",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "于是我们离岛远避至伊吾国，伊吾国国王聘我们当国师，渐渐把公主的往事淡忘。谁知我们不去找七情魔替公主泄恨，他们却找上我们报那断腿之恨，他们自以为练成阵法后不怕催眠术，结果还是被制，那时只当公主的仇恨可以报……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 92,
      "line_end": 94
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yuan_si_min",
      "speaker_name": "原思敏",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "你这小子打他妈的抱不平，告诉你还不听，硬要知道有什么仇恨，我们好意思说出公主被辱的丑事吗？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 96,
      "line_end": 98
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yuan_si_cong",
      "speaker_name": "原思聪",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "那日离去时我说过一句凡事皆因强出头，到时招得祸满身的话，今天你就承当多事的祸害吧！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 100,
      "line_end": 100
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_yuan_si_cong",
      "text": "你们要怎的？",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 104,
      "line_end": 104
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_yuan_si_cong",
      "text": "快滚开！我有急事，要是敢拦着我的去路，剑下绝不容情！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 110,
      "line_end": 112
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_yi_nv_zi",
      "speaker_name": "花衣女子",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "你不能走呀！你不能再弃开我呀……",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 114,
      "line_end": 116
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_yi_nv_zi",
      "speaker_name": "花衣女子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "从今后就再也不会离开我啦。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 122,
      "line_end": 124
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yuan_si_cong",
      "speaker_name": "原思聪",
      "listener": "char_hua_yi_nv_zi",
      "text": "公主，这人不是章痴，交给属下处置吧。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 130,
      "line_end": 130
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_yi_nv_zi",
      "speaker_name": "花衣女子",
      "listener": "char_yuan_si_cong",
      "text": "谁说他不是章痴，他就是烧成了灰我也认识，你是谁，快快出去不要打扰我们。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 132,
      "line_end": 134
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_yi_nv_zi",
      "speaker_name": "花衣女子",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "你怎么只知睡觉，也不跟我说话呀？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 142,
      "line_end": 142
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_yi_nv_zi",
      "speaker_name": "花衣女子",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "醒来，醒来，跟我说话嘛。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 146,
      "line_end": 146
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_yi_nv_zi",
      "speaker_name": "花衣女子",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "你不再爱我，所以不跟我说话吗，以前你天天说爱我，赞我比天仙还美，现在怎么一句话也不说？",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 148,
      "line_end": 150
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_yi_nv_zi",
      "speaker_name": "花衣女子",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "你就再说一句爱我的话，也不成吗？",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 152,
      "line_end": 154
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yuan_si_cong",
      "speaker_name": "原思聪",
      "listener": "char_hua_yi_nv_zi",
      "text": "他不是章痴，所以不会说爱你的话，要是章痴早就说啦。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 156,
      "line_end": 156
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_yi_nv_zi",
      "speaker_name": "花衣女子",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "对啦，对啦，你不是他，你不是他……",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 160,
      "line_end": 160
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_yi_nv_zi",
      "speaker_name": "花衣女子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他不会回来了，他不会回来了，他将我抛弃了……",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 162,
      "line_end": 162
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yuan_si_min",
      "speaker_name": "原思敏",
      "listener": "char_yuan_si_cong",
      "text": "咱们要消恨，就把他丢到大海喂鱼去。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 170,
      "line_end": 170
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yuan_si_cong",
      "speaker_name": "原思聪",
      "listener": "char_yuan_si_min",
      "text": "好，把他丢到海里去。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 172,
      "line_end": 172
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "叶青",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他怎么啦？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 178,
      "line_end": 178
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yuan_si_cong",
      "speaker_name": "原思聪",
      "listener": "char_ye_qing",
      "text": "郡主问的是他吗？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 180,
      "line_end": 180
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "叶青",
      "listener": "char_yuan_si_cong",
      "text": "当然是他，还会有另外一人。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 182,
      "line_end": 182
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yuan_si_cong",
      "speaker_name": "原思聪",
      "listener": "char_ye_qing",
      "text": "此人是公主的大仇人，公主用迷魂巾迷倒他捆了起来，吩咐咱将他丢进大海里去。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 184,
      "line_end": 186
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "叶青",
      "listener": "char_yuan_si_cong",
      "text": "你们把我当做小孩子骗吗，我姐姐神智不清岂会叫你们把他丢到海里，况且你们知道他是谁？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 188,
      "line_end": 188
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yuan_si_cong",
      "speaker_name": "原思聪",
      "listener": "char_ye_qing",
      "text": "公主虽然神智不清，但确实下命叫咱们把他丢到海里，至于他是谁，咱们只知道是公主的仇人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 192,
      "line_end": 194
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "叶青",
      "listener": "char_yuan_si_cong",
      "text": "难道你们不知他是爹爹的上客，我的救命恩人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 196,
      "line_end": 196
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yuan_si_cong",
      "speaker_name": "原思聪",
      "listener": "char_ye_qing",
      "text": "不知道，不知道，咱们前天才回归岛上，岛上的情形还不清楚。",
      "tone": "慌张",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 198,
      "line_end": 200
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "叶青",
      "listener": "char_yuan_si_min",
      "text": "不知者不罪。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 202,
      "line_end": 202
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "叶青",
      "listener": "char_yuan_si_cong",
      "text": "好了，这里没你们的事，快出去。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 208,
      "line_end": 208
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_huai_xuan",
      "speaker_name": "简怀萱",
      "listener": "char_ye_qing",
      "text": "青姐，你快来看看。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 212,
      "line_end": 214
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_huai_xuan",
      "speaker_name": "简怀萱",
      "listener": "char_ye_qing",
      "text": "大哥不要紧吗？",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 216,
      "line_end": 216
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "叶青",
      "listener": "char_jian_huai_xuan",
      "text": "他被迷魂香迷住倒不要紧，只是……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 220,
      "line_end": 220
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_huai_xuan",
      "speaker_name": "简怀萱",
      "listener": "char_ye_qing",
      "text": "只是什么？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 222,
      "line_end": 222
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "叶青",
      "listener": "char_jian_huai_xuan",
      "text": "他手足上的绳索无法解开。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 224,
      "line_end": 224
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_huai_xuan",
      "speaker_name": "简怀萱",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "有没有剪刀？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 230,
      "line_end": 230
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "叶青",
      "listener": "char_jian_huai_xuan",
      "text": "别费心啦，就是宝刀宝剑也不能割断。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 232,
      "line_end": 232
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "叶青",
      "listener": "char_jian_huai_xuan",
      "text": "这些绳结天下只有我爹爹解得开，姐姐早向爹学过，如今神智不清会结不一定会解。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 236,
      "line_end": 238
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_huai_xuan",
      "speaker_name": "简怀萱",
      "listener": "char_ye_qing",
      "text": "那赶紧去找你爹爹解吧！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 240,
      "line_end": 240
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "叶青",
      "listener": "char_jian_huai_xuan",
      "text": "怎能去找爹爹，爹爹说要杀他，送他去求爹爹，还不是送他去死。",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 242,
      "line_end": 244
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_huai_xuan",
      "speaker_name": "简怀萱",
      "listener": "char_ye_qing",
      "text": "那怎么办呢？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 246,
      "line_end": 246
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "叶青",
      "listener": "char_jian_huai_xuan",
      "text": "目前先救他离岛要紧，萱妹，你抱着他随我来。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 248,
      "line_end": 249
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_shi_mou",
      "speaker_name": "叶士谋",
      "listener": "char_ye_qing",
      "text": "到哪里去？",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 250,
      "line_end": 250
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "叶青",
      "listener": "char_ye_shi_mou",
      "text": "爹爹……你老人家来这里做什么……",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 252,
      "line_end": 253
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_shi_mou",
      "speaker_name": "叶士谋",
      "listener": "char_ye_qing",
      "text": "你来做什么，爹就来做什么。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 254,
      "line_end": 255
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_huai_xuan",
      "speaker_name": "简怀萱",
      "listener": "char_ye_shi_mou",
      "text": "咱们来救我大哥，你也来救他吗？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 258,
      "line_end": 259
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_shi_mou",
      "speaker_name": "叶士谋",
      "listener": "char_jian_huai_xuan",
      "text": "快把你大哥还给我。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 262,
      "line_end": 262
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "叶青",
      "listener": "char_ye_shi_mou",
      "text": "爹爹，你不能杀他，他是女儿的救命恩人，你要杀他就杀我吧。",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 266,
      "line_end": 267
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_shi_mou",
      "speaker_name": "叶士谋",
      "listener": "char_ye_qing",
      "text": "他就对你那么重要？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 270,
      "line_end": 270
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "叶青",
      "listener": "char_ye_shi_mou",
      "text": "知恩图报，爹要是杀了他，女儿怎生对得起人家！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 272,
      "line_end": 272
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_shi_mou",
      "speaker_name": "叶士谋",
      "listener": "char_ye_qing",
      "text": "谁说我要杀他啦？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 274,
      "line_end": 274
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "叶青",
      "listener": "char_ye_shi_mou",
      "text": "爹自己说的，爹说决不能让外人来到岛上，而他所以来到岛上，是女儿邀请来的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 276,
      "line_end": 278
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_shi_mou",
      "speaker_name": "叶士谋",
      "listener": "char_ye_qing",
      "text": "我不杀他，你快把他递给爹，一个女孩子抱着大男人成什么体统。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 280,
      "line_end": 281
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "叶青",
      "listener": "char_ye_shi_mou",
      "text": "不，不，爹爹骗我，不能递给你。",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 284,
      "line_end": 285
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_shi_mou",
      "speaker_name": "叶士谋",
      "listener": "char_ye_qing",
      "text": "还不递来，要讨打吗？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 288,
      "line_end": 288
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "叶青",
      "listener": "char_ye_shi_mou",
      "text": "你杀了我吧，女儿自幼没娘，也没人疼我，反正活着也没意思啦……",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 290,
      "line_end": 291
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_shi_mou",
      "speaker_name": "叶士谋",
      "listener": "char_ye_qing",
      "text": "你的脾气跟你娘一样的倔烈，孩子，我不会杀他的，你想他能从不归谷出来，我还会杀他吗？",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 292,
      "line_end": 294
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "叶青",
      "listener": "char_ye_shi_mou",
      "text": "啊，我怎么忘了，他能从不归谷出来，爹就不会杀他了。",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 296,
      "line_end": 297
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_shi_mou",
      "speaker_name": "叶士谋",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "果然像，果然像，像极了。",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 306,
      "line_end": 308
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "叶青",
      "listener": "char_ye_shi_mou",
      "text": "爹，你说什么呀？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 310,
      "line_end": 310
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_shi_mou",
      "speaker_name": "叶士谋",
      "listener": "char_ye_qing",
      "text": "简召舞说他与自己相像，陆文兰也说他像，我总不信，今日亲眼看到，不由得不信天下有这等相像的人！",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 312,
      "line_end": 314
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "叶青",
      "listener": "char_ye_shi_mou",
      "text": "像谁呀？什么人长得和他一样呀？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 318,
      "line_end": 320
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_shi_mou",
      "speaker_name": "叶士谋",
      "listener": "char_ye_qing",
      "text": "你不认识，那人是天池府的主人，名叫简召舞。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 322,
      "line_end": 322
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_huai_xuan",
      "speaker_name": "简怀萱",
      "listener": "char_ye_shi_mou",
      "text": "他不是天池府的主人，他不是天池府的主人……",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 324,
      "line_end": 324
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_shi_mou",
      "speaker_name": "叶士谋",
      "listener": "char_jian_huai_xuan",
      "text": "简召舞是你大哥，天池府一脉单传的继承者，你做妹妹的难道不承认吗？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 326,
      "line_end": 328
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_huai_xuan",
      "speaker_name": "简怀萱",
      "listener": "char_ye_shi_mou",
      "text": "他杀死我母亲，杀死我二哥，我再也不认他……",
      "tone": "悲痛",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 330,
      "line_end": 330
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_shi_mou",
      "speaker_name": "叶士谋",
      "listener": "char_jian_huai_xuan",
      "text": "你这丫头真没良心，简召舞白疼你了，那日简召舞杀死要害他的后母，杀死要阴谋夺取天池府产业的弟弟，惟独不忍心杀你，就因平日疼爱你，你还不知道吗？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 332,
      "line_end": 334
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_huai_xuan",
      "speaker_name": "简怀萱",
      "listener": "char_ye_shi_mou",
      "text": "谁要他疼爱，我决不原谅他，还有你，你！你是帮凶，是杀我全家，令我家破人亡的帮凶！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 336,
      "line_end": 338
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_shi_mou",
      "speaker_name": "叶士谋",
      "listener": "char_jian_huai_xuan",
      "text": "臭丫头，你敢对我不敬，非给你吃点苦头。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 340,
      "line_end": 340
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_shi_mou",
      "speaker_name": "叶士谋",
      "listener": "char_ye_qing",
      "text": "谁要你挡啦，滚开，滚开！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 348,
      "line_end": 348
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "叶青",
      "listener": "char_ye_shi_mou",
      "text": "爹，你忘了说过决不为难她的话吗？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 350,
      "line_end": 350
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_shi_mou",
      "speaker_name": "叶士谋",
      "listener": "char_ye_qing",
      "text": "青儿，爹昏头昏脑打错到你，痛不痛？",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 354,
      "line_end": 355
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "叶青",
      "listener": "char_ye_shi_mou",
      "text": "不痛，就是打痛了，爹打女儿也是应该的。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 358,
      "line_end": 358
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_shi_mou",
      "speaker_name": "叶士谋",
      "listener": "char_ye_qing",
      "text": "这些绳结是你姐姐结的吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 360,
      "line_end": 362
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "叶青",
      "listener": "char_ye_shi_mou",
      "text": "缚龙索为天下绝技，爹只传过姐姐，除她外还会是谁结的？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 364,
      "line_end": 365
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_shi_mou",
      "speaker_name": "叶士谋",
      "listener": "char_ye_qing",
      "text": "白儿神智疯颠竟尚未忘缚龙索的结法，难得，难得！",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 368,
      "line_end": 369
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "叶青",
      "listener": "char_ye_shi_mou",
      "text": "姐姐病了这多年总不见好，爹爹，难道就让姐姐这样终身下去？",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 372,
      "line_end": 373
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_shi_mou",
      "speaker_name": "叶士谋",
      "listener": "char_ye_qing",
      "text": "为父终生钻研慑魂术，结果自己女儿的疯颠却无法治，莫非是老天的惩罚，给我的一个报应？",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 376,
      "line_end": 377
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "叶青",
      "listener": "char_ye_shi_mou",
      "text": "姐姐的疯颠并非中术，是故爹爹无法治好，这只有精通医术的人才能治，女儿认为一个人定可治好姐的病症。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 380,
      "line_end": 381
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_shi_mou",
      "speaker_name": "叶士谋",
      "listener": "char_ye_qing",
      "text": "是谁？他若能将白儿治好，为父一定重重酬谢他。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 384,
      "line_end": 384
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "叶青",
      "listener": "char_ye_shi_mou",
      "text": "就是他，他能治好女儿的绝症，医术堪称天下无二，爹快将他醒转，解开绳索，请他救治姐姐。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 386,
      "line_end": 387
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_shi_mou",
      "speaker_name": "叶士谋",
      "listener": "char_ye_qing",
      "text": "他被你姐姐迷魂香迷倒，醒转不难，但这绳……却不能立时解开。",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 390,
      "line_end": 391
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "叶青",
      "listener": "char_ye_shi_mou",
      "text": "为什么啊？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 392,
      "line_end": 392
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_shi_mou",
      "speaker_name": "叶士谋",
      "listener": "char_ye_qing",
      "text": "简召舞说他武功虽强，但性格却与吾辈大不相容，只怕放了他一定对咱们不利，暂时要考虑考虑，孟浪不得。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 394,
      "line_end": 396
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "叶青",
      "listener": "char_ye_shi_mou",
      "text": "爹爹这般听简召舞的话？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 398,
      "line_end": 399
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_shi_mou",
      "speaker_name": "叶士谋",
      "listener": "char_ye_qing",
      "text": "我深知简召舞的为人精明干练，他的话不可不信，万一放了芮玮，纵虎归山，再要擒时就难矣。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 400,
      "line_end": 402
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "叶青",
      "listener": "char_ye_shi_mou",
      "text": "爹，你查出是谁泄漏本岛的秘密，以致七剑派联合起来对付咱们？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 404,
      "line_end": 405
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_shi_mou",
      "speaker_name": "叶士谋",
      "listener": "char_ye_qing",
      "text": "七剑派门下一一被擒来本岛之事，只有十三铁卫知晓，他们对我忠心不二，实令我想不出内奸会是谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 408,
      "line_end": 409
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "叶青",
      "listener": "char_ye_shi_mou",
      "text": "简召舞也知道吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 412,
      "line_end": 412
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_shi_mou",
      "speaker_name": "叶士谋",
      "listener": "char_ye_qing",
      "text": "我曾向他说过，他与我同有称霸武林之心，所以这些事情对他并不隐瞒，而天池府在武林中尚颇有潜力，为父还想利用他，将来以便扩充自己的势力。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 414,
      "line_end": 415
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "叶青",
      "listener": "char_ye_shi_mou",
      "text": "爹想到利用他，他就不会利用爹吗，以女儿看来这泄漏秘密的人一定就是他，这叫做坐山观虎斗，然后来个渔翁得利呀……",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 418,
      "line_end": 419
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_shi_mou",
      "speaker_name": "叶士谋",
      "listener": "char_ye_qing",
      "text": "不要乱说，他不是这种人！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 421,
      "line_end": 421
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "叶青",
      "listener": "char_ye_shi_mou",
      "text": "他也是想独霸武林，岂能容得下爹爹，等到七剑派与魔鬼岛两败俱伤后，这天下就是他的了……",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 422,
      "line_end": 423
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_shi_mou",
      "speaker_name": "叶士谋",
      "listener": "char_ye_qing",
      "text": "叫你不要乱说，就不要再说啦！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 424,
      "line_end": 424
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "叶青",
      "listener": "char_ye_shi_mou",
      "text": "爹要相信他还不如相信芮大哥，他比简召舞忠厚老实多了……",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 428,
      "line_end": 428
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_shi_mou",
      "speaker_name": "叶士谋",
      "listener": "char_ye_qing",
      "text": "我看人决不会错，简召舞一定不会出卖我，况且我帮他争得天池府产业，他一辈子永远感激我。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 430,
      "line_end": 431
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "叶青",
      "listener": "char_ye_shi_mou",
      "text": "简召舞此人为了争得产业不惜杀母杀弟，这种人呀，无情无义，什么坏事做不出来．爹呀，你千万小心！",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 434,
      "line_end": 435
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_shi_mou",
      "speaker_name": "叶士谋",
      "listener": "char_ye_qing",
      "text": "死丫头，别说啦！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 436,
      "line_end": 436
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "叶青",
      "listener": "char_ye_shi_mou",
      "text": "依女儿猜简召舞离开本岛后一定会招引七剑派高手来攻打本岛……",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 438,
      "line_end": 439
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yuan_si_cong",
      "speaker_name": "原思聪",
      "listener": "char_ye_shi_mou",
      "text": "岛主，有三艘快船向本岛驶来！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 448,
      "line_end": 449
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_shi_mou",
      "speaker_name": "叶士谋",
      "listener": "char_yuan_si_cong",
      "text": "是不是商船？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 452,
      "line_end": 452
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yuan_si_cong",
      "speaker_name": "原思聪",
      "listener": "char_ye_shi_mou",
      "text": "不是，船身吃水甚浅，不可能是装载货物的商船。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 454,
      "line_end": 454
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "叶青",
      "listener": "char_yuan_si_cong",
      "text": "船上情况如何？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 456,
      "line_end": 456
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yuan_si_cong",
      "speaker_name": "原思聪",
      "listener": "char_ye_qing",
      "text": "每艘船头站着七位劲装的大汉，其中有僧有道……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 458,
      "line_end": 458
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "叶青",
      "listener": "char_ye_shi_mou",
      "text": "爹，不错啦，一定就是简召舞引来的七剑派高手，他们七人一处，分明就是练好的七星阵。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 460,
      "line_end": 461
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_shi_mou",
      "speaker_name": "叶士谋",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "哈哈！好小子果真出卖我。",
      "tone": "狂笑",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 464,
      "line_end": 464
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_shi_mou",
      "speaker_name": "叶士谋",
      "listener": "char_yuan_si_cong",
      "text": "把他好好关起来，等咱们退敌后再来问他。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 466,
      "line_end": 467
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "叶青",
      "listener": "char_ye_shi_mou",
      "text": "爹，他们的七星阵十分厉害，还是芮大哥醒转请他相助的好。",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 470,
      "line_end": 471
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_shi_mou",
      "speaker_name": "叶士谋",
      "listener": "char_ye_qing",
      "text": "此人决不会助我，况且七星阵不见得难到咱们。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 474,
      "line_end": 474
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_huai_xuan",
      "speaker_name": "简怀萱",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "开门！开门！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 482,
      "line_end": 482
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yuan_si_min",
      "speaker_name": "原思敏",
      "listener": "char_jian_huai_xuan",
      "text": "等咱们退敌后再放你出来。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 484,
      "line_end": 484
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_huai_xuan",
      "speaker_name": "简怀萱",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们把我大哥关到哪里去？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 486,
      "line_end": 486
    }
